---
import avatar_image from "../../../assets/images/Memoji.png";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<div
  class="card group overflow-hidden transfor-y-[-40%] bg-gradient-to-b from-zinc-50 to-zinc-300 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-300 dark:bg-gradient-to-b dark:from-zinc-800 dark:to-zinc-900 shadow-lg rounded-lg border border-neutral-400 dark:border-neutral-700 hover:border-zinc-900 dark:hover:border-zinc-200 align-start flex-none h-full justify-start relative transform perspective-1200 w-full col-span-1 md:col-span-3 md:row-span-4 p-6 hover:scale-[1.01] transition-transform delay-500 duration-300 ease-in-out"
>
  <h1
    class="text-md font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-300 self-start justify-center"
  >
    About Me
  </h1>
  <div class="flex w-full h-full">
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-between md:max-h-[300px] gap-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col h-full gap-2">
        <p class="m-0 font-light text-xl">
          With <b class="font-semibold"
            >2 years+ of experience in being a Software Engineer</b
          >, My comprehensive expertise covers the the entire development
          lifecycle, including infrastructure, front-end, back-end programming,
          and especially test automation.
        </p>
        <p class="m-0 font-light text-xl">
          I enjoy creating well-organized folder structures and writing
          efficient, maintainable code. Challenging projects that push me to
          grow and improve are where I excel."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <Image
      width="300"
      height="300"
      src={avatar_image}
      class="w-auto max-h-[300px] select-none absolute right-[-90px] bottom-[-20px] z-[-1] opacity-50 lg:opacity-100 lg:relative lg:right-auto lg:bottom-auto lg:z-auto pointer-events-none"
      alt="Norris Memoji"
    />
  </div>
</div>
